<div class="container container--narrow" style="padding-top: var(--space-120); padding-bottom: var(--space-120);">
  <h1 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-64);">About AERIDIAN</h1>
  
  <div class="brand-manifesto" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-120); text-align: center;">
    <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-24);">Manifesto</h2>
    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: var(--font-body-large); line-height: 1.8; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
      AERIDIAN operates at the intersection of technical utility and architectural precision. We reject the compromise between extreme performance and high aesthetics. Our garments are engineered systems, designed to perform in hostile urban conditions while maintaining an absolute, minimalist silhouette.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid--2-col" style="gap: var(--space-64); margin-bottom: var(--space-120);">
    <div>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-24);">Philosophy</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">
        Function does not precede form; they are synthesized. Every panel is drafted with mathematical rigor. Every seam is ultrasonic-welded for aerodynamic integrity. We do not design clothing; we construct atmospheric equipment.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      {{ 'collection-1' | placeholder_svg_tag: 'placeholder-svg' }}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid--2-col" style="gap: var(--space-64); margin-bottom: var(--space-120);">
    <div style="order: 2;">
      <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-24);">Material Science</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">
        We develop proprietary composite fabrics in collaboration with advanced textile laboratories globally. The resulting materials—hyper-breathable armors and kinetic weather-resistant membranes—defy traditional categorizations. Built to last a lifetime.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div style="order: 1;">
      {{ 'collection-2' | placeholder_svg_tag: 'placeholder-svg' }}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "About AERIDIAN",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
